title: Missing corrdinates for "Etelä-Pohjanmaan vaakuna". Page with the location not found.
details: Tried pages: Etelä-Pohjanmaan, Etelä-Pohjanmaa, Etelä-Pohjanmaan maakunta.
You can check if there is a potential way to automate it: scripts/heraldry/utils/fetch-data-smart.ts.
Or just tell the tool which page name to use in scripts/heraldry/utils/constants.ts.
You will find the proper name of the page in the URL, make sure it has lat and lon.
Missing corrdinates for "Etelä-Pohjanmaa". Page exists but without location, tried related "Seinäjoki". But it failed.
Missing corrdinates for "Etelä-Pohjanmaan maakunta". Page exists but without location, tried related "Seinäjoki". But it failed.
